item.description:
@Java_Is_My_Bitch wrote:

You mean like a portal, to take you there?

I suggest going to the teleto Method:

search Teleto in client.java

Pick a teleport that you know you WON’T use, and change the coordinate to the jad training area.

Also Under Update(); OR Initialize method, you can put a sendFrame so it can tell users that this teleport will teleport you to jad instead of the original teleport that it was, but i am not familiar with the interfaceid’s for those 2, so i guess you have to find them out.
